Class - It is design/blueprint/template of an object

      Class can contains:
        1)Variables / Properties
        2)Methods / Action
        3)Constructor

Object - instance of class, object exist physically in the memory

      Syntax to create object:
        1)ClassName objName = new ClassName();

Constructor - To initialize class variables

       Rules of the Constructor:
         1)Constructor name should be same as the class name
         2)It must not have any return type
         3)It will get call automatically when we create object of the class

